WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:19.110 --> 00:21.911
Don't do it.

00:21.946 --> 00:23.780
Please.

00:23.814 --> 00:25.081
We're almost home.

00:25.149 --> 00:27.917
There's no home.
Not yet.

00:34.391 --> 00:36.793
We haven't eaten
in three days.

00:45.302 --> 00:47.403
Dan, you all right?

00:47.471 --> 00:51.141
Yeah, yeah. I'm fine.
Let's keep moving.

01:04.522 --> 01:06.890
There's no one here.

01:12.563 --> 01:15.865
It's a message from Hal.

01:15.900 --> 01:17.600
See,
I told you he'd be fine.

01:20.437 --> 01:22.539
Hal's telling us
they had to leave.

01:22.573 --> 01:24.874
Those numbers
should tell us where they went.

01:24.942 --> 01:27.377
Why don't we try to
scare up some food

01:27.411 --> 01:29.879
while you
decipher the message?

01:36.120 --> 01:39.422
Hey, Dad.
What are you looking at?

01:39.456 --> 01:42.926
Uh, coordinates.

01:42.960 --> 01:46.129
Longitude and latitude.

01:46.163 --> 01:49.299
30 miles
to the southwest.

01:49.333 --> 01:51.134
Right there.

01:51.168 --> 01:54.170
Hmm. Another hike.
We can do it.

01:54.205 --> 01:55.672
What do you think's
over there?

01:55.706 --> 01:57.106
I don't know.

01:57.141 --> 01:59.275
"Croatoan"
implies that Hal

01:59.310 --> 02:01.177
took everybody
to a safer place.

02:01.212 --> 02:03.046
I suggest
we go join them.

02:04.448 --> 02:06.316
<i> A place of...</i>

02:06.350 --> 02:09.219
<i>All will...</i>

02:09.252 --> 02:12.255
<i>...26.</i>

02:46.737 --> 02:49.125
<i>All will be welcome.</i>

02:55.132 --> 02:57.100
<i>A place of peace.</i>

03:51.230 --> 03:55.230
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Falling Skies 4x05 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Mind Wars</font>
